    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Shifter Style Aspect</strong><br/><br/><p>You gain a bonus on damage rolls while prone equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum +0). You can crawl up to half your speed as a move action. At 8th level, whenever a creature provokes an attack of opportunity from you, that creature is considered flatfooted against your attack. At 15th level, whenever you take a 5-foot step, you are treated as if you were still in your original space for the purposes of flanking others until the start of your next turn (though you can't use this aspect to provide flanking for yourself), and you can crawl up to your full speed as a move action.</p>",
